ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend the class to other students as is a good overview of several important topics in microbial pathogenesis.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Provided a good overview of several area and made me more aware of the research being done in labs in the department.

This course definitely provided a strong overview of microbial pathogenesis; it should probably be required for all Micro-track students. It helped me understand the research that is going on within the department.
